usens De pace, ist der Forschung bislang entgangen. Hier setzt die Studie an und fragt danach, welche positiven Friedensvorstellungen und -konzepte damals existierten.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aPeacexHistoryy17th century. 0aThirty Years' War, 1618-1648xPeace. 4aDreißigjähriger Krieg. 4aFriedenskonzepte in der Frühen Neuzeit. 4aNicolaus Schaffshausen. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 17th Century.2bisacsh  aNicolaus Schaffshausen.  aThirty Years War.  aconcepts of peace in the early modern era.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1z978311076248808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018z9783110603149oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831105807470 cprintz978311058062440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311058338040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110583380423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110583380/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-076248-8  DG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017